{"tid":1643613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓國瑜公布「兩岸政策白皮書」 反對一國兩制和台獨","createTime":"2019-10-10T08:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T02:16:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d34ae1e51b5e96da86ac7f998244cf88cca413","tid":1643613,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:08:26.000Z","msg":"在台灣，國民黨總統候選人韓國瑜公布「兩岸政策白皮書」。他表示，一定要捍衛主權，堅持「一中各表的九二共識」、兩岸重建互信，恢復「兩岸對話架構」、建立台灣朝野對話機制，形成兩岸政策內部共識，以及以台灣民主化經驗，為大陸的政治改革提供借鏡，只有大陸民主化，才能確保兩岸真正和平發展。<br />\n韓國瑜公布的白皮書反對「一國兩制」、反對台獨，支持香港人追求自由與民主，呼籲大陸政府尊重香港人的訴求，並落實「港人治港」理念。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83-%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E7%99%BD%E7%9A%AE%E6%9B%B8-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%B0%E7%8D%A8-051924980.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2591%259C%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25AD%2596%25E7%2599%25BD%25E7%259A%25AE%25E6%259B%25B8-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%258D%25A8-051924980.html&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=8052e72c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83-%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E7%99%BD%E7%9A%AE%E6%9B%B8-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%B0%E7%8D%A8-051924980.html</a>"},{"pid":"a604f2eaccc752d8dd1c9b963fe944f2108c8d64","tid":1643613,"uid":94828,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:11:05.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜：反對一國兩制 支持一國一制"},{"pid":"fb8bc51261b511f4f18387453e62ec9509965318","tid":1643613,"uid":35930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:12:04.000Z","msg":"扮乜鳩丫屌"},{"pid":"45f88a3fe21a06139db306e514159eb7076db5e4","tid":1643613,"uid":196625,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:12:51.000Z","msg":"返屋企餵狗啦佢"},{"pid":"eac67af9c2f58163a67cdfffa5627c9c0d535246","tid":1643613,"uid":90180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:14:27.000Z","msg":"所謂九二共識等於，兩個共識，各自表述。"},{"pid":"f5d2714816fd7721192560b0fb96be1296d9cb93","tid":1643613,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:24:30.000Z","msg":"ＣＨＩ　ＮＡ都講明唔接受各自表述，重要拎嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22b5bf5d9ffeed793c95e8baf65654f866a3d30","tid":1643613,"uid":8562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"反對「一國兩制」、反對台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nON99"},{"pid":"b981eb483997af871f66aae634576fb95bc3a6f4","tid":1643613,"uid":31863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e22b5bf5d9ffeed793c95e8baf65654f866a3d30","tid":1643613,"uid":8562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"反對「一國兩制」、反對台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nON99"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"即係想一國一制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3821794bcde664a3573fcf62cd31a6c57bb1154f","tid":1643613,"uid":224510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e22b5bf5d9ffeed793c95e8baf65654f866a3d30","tid":1643613,"uid":8562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"反對「一國兩制」、反對台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nON99"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"香港冇一國兩制就係港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0452ad004d1a16c9d941d4e69e566afbac59640b","tid":1643613,"uid":22535,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"佢贊成一國一制"},{"pid":"5805318a0a4536765c91f72368182a566aa5300b","tid":1643613,"uid":286018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"反對「一國兩制」、反對台獨<br />\n姐係想一國一制 想回歸中國囉<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"d07708d3544af300b5ddf6e7550a5061371917a6","tid":1643613,"uid":402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:31:26.000Z","msg":"佢成家都係大話精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955e5c10c540fbab2b9503ab54e42afe52fa01d4","tid":1643613,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:32:53.000Z","msg":"反攻大陸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d6d5e2adecabb8324de0a7b5ffb3de52369bce","tid":1643613,"uid":259493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:33:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n要攬炒、炒到盡！2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[ 戰略物資管制 +美國要求獨立調查委員會]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strategic_and_Critical_Materials_Stock_Piling_Act_of_1939\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FStrategic_and_Critical_Materials_Stock_Piling_Act_of_1939&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=0f13edbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strategic_and_Critical_Materials_Stock_Piling_Act_of_1939</a><br />\n二次世界大戰之中，美國透過此法案阻撓戰略物資進入日本/德國<br />\n人權法案審議中，為了增加美國支持  我們必須做好英文Fact checked 事件表/YouTube影片，做好時序 每星期發生的暴行 ，寄給國會議員！<br />\n'人權民主法案'只是開始，一定要每年不斷加辣加法案，直至真普選和永遠廢除中聯辦， 高度自治才可以保護外國人在香港的資產/金融財產；<br />\n違反中英聯合聲明就要中國付出代價，美國要對中國和香港進行戰略物資管制 ，必須有兩普選+ 獨立調查委員會+ 取消駐港的中聯辦和港澳版， 才考慮取消全面禁運<br />\n身在美國/加拿大的手足 必須親身拜訪 國會議員！（女性或學生演講為佳）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[ 所有已發展國要求成立獨立調查委員會+ 全球制裁央企和偽民企 +歐盟調查央企/偽民企的反競爭情況一如對付google壟斷一樣]<br />\n身處歐洲/日本/ 加拿大/英國/瑞士 的手足！（女性或學生演講為佳），請要求當地議員提出當地的人權及民主法案，支援香港呼應美國，親身拜訪當地國會議員， 連霸權美國都咁支持香港, 其他國家 ,道德上 需要響應; <br />\n違反中英聯合聲明就要中國付出代價， 要求歐/日調查央企/偽民企的一切罪行， 反壟斷法/傾銷/反競爭/國家補貼 /商業間諜， google和微軟都可以被歐盟庭處罰 中國冇可能不守約束<br />\n中國的戰略物資管制， 貿易戰開始後，中國更加依賴日本/歐洲/英國的技術， 中國的商業間諜罪行無處不在， 絕對可以要求大陸停止干預香港，否則即時制裁。<br />\n<br />\n各國要解決香港危機， 必先成立獨立調查委員會， 把中共的醜惡公諸於世 ， 世人譁然 就 所有制裁和稅行都變得合理， 也名正言順地保障各國在內地在香港的利益。<br />\n<br />\n謹記&ldquo;不要問：為何他們無動於衷 ，不幫助我們，請先問為何他們一定要幫助我們？&rdquo; 我們既要謙虛也要感恩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人幫外國人食子彈，就是保護全球經濟增長、他們在香港的利益和 自由陣營的最前線 ，眼前的'新西柏林'意義重大，西方國家更沒理由， 無條件輸送金錢給中國請流氓打柒香港人， 今時今日，孕婦和十幾歲的學生都在前線捍衛著自由，人類道德價值觀最高的歐洲，是否應該幫助香港人<br />\n<br />\n再冇其他選擇 香港人不講獨立不分化<br />\n一齊頂硬上！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9ed9372d8310c70ea36c8da770603aab0e0e7c4d","tid":1643613,"uid":24074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"咁似啲藍扮黃果啲鋪頭，自尋死路啦"},{"pid":"a1a6dda513f880dbc763f3a412d3234fe064dc41","tid":1643613,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ed9372d8310c70ea36c8da770603aab0e0e7c4d","tid":1643613,"uid":24074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"咁似啲藍扮黃果啲鋪頭，自尋死路啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:26:09.000Z","msg":"根本就同一類人"},{"pid":"a0f14e561b3b79869ae10ba2007aa5f652af66fd","tid":1643613,"uid":34517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5805318a0a4536765c91f72368182a566aa5300b","tid":1643613,"uid":286018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"反對「一國兩制」、反對台獨<br />\n姐係想一國一制 想回歸中國囉<br />\n屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:31:01.000Z","msg":"可以解讀為反攻大陸既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三十年前"},{"pid":"b1e9bfb8838dd567cb00744b90a5f6dcb35116f2","tid":1643613,"uid":315502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20